        <body>
            <div1 xml:id="d001" type="work" decls="#md" met="various">
                <head>
                    <title>1</title>
                    <bibl source="digital">Marcello Montalto</bibl>
                </head>
                <div2 xml:id="001c001" type="carmen" met="H">
                    <head>
                        <abbr>1</abbr>
                    </head>
                    <p xml:id="d001l1" n="tit.">ad virginem Venetam Cassandram Fidelem philosophantem | Franciscus Ubertus</p>
                    <l xml:id="d001l2" n="1">Sis felix, nostrumque leves, Cassandra, laborem</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l3" n="2">Ac mihi qua sit iter, ducat quod fontis ad undam</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l4" n="3">Pierii, monstrare velis. Nam virgo per aequor</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l5" n="4">Venimus, ut liceat doctas audire sorores</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l6" n="5">Si datur hoc per te facilis modo Nympha roganti,</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l7" n="6">Qualiscumque canet laudes tibi nostra Thalia.</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l8" n="7">Nam sexum super egressa es virtute, virago,</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l9" n="8">Tum celeri (mirum) studio. Hinc doctissima dici</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l10" n="9">Iure potes; sed quam memorem te, virgo pudica?</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l11" n="10">An quae diva? Refer. An quae tu forte Sibylla?</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l12" n="11">Eveniunt quando haec divum haud sine numine! Nympha,</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l13" n="12">Vive, lege ac magnum scribens tibi nomen adopta.</l>
                    <lb/>
                </div2>
                <div2 xml:id="001c002" type="carmen" met="E">
                    <head>
                        <abbr>2</abbr>
                    </head>
                    <p xml:id="d001l14" n="tit.">ad virginem Venetam Cassandram Fidelem philosophantem | Franciscus Ubertus</p>
                    <l xml:id="d001l15" n="1">Virginei Cassandra chori doctissima virgo</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l16" n="2">O princeps sexus gloria et huius have!</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l17" n="3">Flaminius de te noster miranda canebat;</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l18" n="4">Ut sunt, illa mihi credere libet.</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l19" n="5">Vera quidem credens mirorque et gratulor urbi</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l20" n="6">Quae te progenuit candida virgo tuae.</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l21" n="7">Quid ni? Splendor enim patriae Cassandra potentis</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l22" n="8">Si cadat infelix; si modo livor, eris.</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l23" n="9">O, quantum est? Doctos facunda ex tempore virgo</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l24" n="10">De studiis audes semper adire viros.</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l25" n="11">Praestat opem Pallas, quam tu colis inclyta Nympha</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l26" n="12">Hinc magni freta es viribus ingenii.</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l27" n="13">Virgo felix Cumeae saecula vatis</l>
                    <l xml:id="d001l28" n="14">O Veneti vivas maxima fama soli.</l>
                </div2>
            </div1>
        </body>
